extraDescription: A contract to assist in the preparation of the Quality Management System (QMS) Gate 2 project documentation and secure approvals through the Department's Investment Management Process. The end state beyond this contract, is the development of a seamless end-to-end Quality Management System (QMS) to modernize quality reviews/conformity studies and ensuring robust payment and processing accuracy and stewardship reviews for Service Canada's three core programs, namely Employment Insurance, Old Age Security and Canada Pension Plan.
